options.text: I am a mighty adventurer. Who are you?
I'm not sure, I was hoping you could tell me.

4b5076df-aa4f-4c93-899a-c0aeedbd9a66.title: <player>
4b5076df-aa4f-4c93-899a-c0aeedbd9a66.text: I was hoping you could tell me.

415c07ac-7491-4543-b9b7-9154f94065d5.title: Sir Prysin
415c07ac-7491-4543-b9b7-9154f94065d5.text: Well I've never met you before.

13fe531b-5571-477c-b9ce-ec16d66e886a.title: <player>
13fe531b-5571-477c-b9ce-ec16d66e886a.text: I am a mighty adventurer, who are you?

2480c883-78e4-4062-8933-2b0c9d13de5a.title: Sir Prysin
2480c883-78e4-4062-8933-2b0c9d13de5a.text:
I am Sir Prysin. A bold and famous knight of the
realm.

options.text: I am a mighty adventurer. Who are you?
I'm not sure, I was hoping you could tell me.
Gypsy Aris said I should come and talk to you.

6bb4c8a1-78de-4a10-bdca-220637b5e7e6.title: <player>
6bb4c8a1-78de-4a10-bdca-220637b5e7e6.text: I was hoping you could tell me.

c9bfeb60-2eba-453c-a034-102db273d6e1.title: Sir Prysin
c9bfeb60-2eba-453c-a034-102db273d6e1.text: Well I've never met you before.

a4d77277-1e9d-45c5-a927-864e8497fe2a.title: <player>
a4d77277-1e9d-45c5-a927-864e8497fe2a.text: I am a mighty adventurer, who are you?

4405a4ac-85f8-4095-9e2e-29cf9137fa96.title: Sir Prysin
4405a4ac-85f8-4095-9e2e-29cf9137fa96.text:
I am Sir Prysin. A bold and famous knight of the
realm.

52f60e29-433a-403e-bce9-47de6be3cdfb.title: <player>
52f60e29-433a-403e-bce9-47de6be3cdfb.text: Gypsy Aris said I should come and talk to you.

0e1e4a41-c016-4885-ae71-229b352cf4ea.title: Sir Prysin
0e1e4a41-c016-4885-ae71-229b352cf4ea.text:
Gypsy Aris? Is she still alive? I remember her from
when I was pretty young. Well what do you need to
talk to me about?

options.text: I need to find Silverlight.
Yes, she is still alive.

a9f777bc-a3bc-44e5-85f5-c856f58556be.title: <player>
a9f777bc-a3bc-44e5-85f5-c856f58556be.text: Yes she is still alive. She lives right outside the castle!

149b4295-cf5f-40fd-a489-f5475198e5e0.title: Sir Prysin
149b4295-cf5f-40fd-a489-f5475198e5e0.text:
Oh, is that the same gypsy? I would have thought she
would have died by now. She was pretty old when I
was a lad.

97eea128-1265-45ec-a616-64bc12c6f492.title: Sir Prysin
97eea128-1265-45ec-a616-64bc12c6f492.text: Anyway, what can I do for you?

a87536b0-0f1d-4729-850b-da32fe63c910.title: Sir Prysin
a87536b0-0f1d-4729-850b-da32fe63c910.text: What do you need to find that for?

dd83da90-265e-40ea-bf3c-400a6eac4541.title: <player>
dd83da90-265e-40ea-bf3c-400a6eac4541.text: I need it to fight Delrith.

c51142d7-b87a-46fa-9201-19379ec23a3b.title: Sir Prysin
c51142d7-b87a-46fa-9201-19379ec23a3b.text:
Delrith? I thought the world was rid of him, thanks to
my great-grandfather.

options.text: Well, the gypsy's crystal ball seems to think otherwise.
He's back and unfortunately I've got to deal with him.

75c87915-93f8-4120-aa80-8aa3777b2800.title: <player>
75c87915-93f8-4120-aa80-8aa3777b2800.text: Well the gypsy's crystal ball seems to think otherwise.

f6bd3899-136b-4de2-864d-45faa6c1639d.title: Sir Prysin
f6bd3899-136b-4de2-864d-45faa6c1639d.text: Well if the ball says so, I'd better help you.

25cfbcd1-f83e-4342-bd69-7cce8f38b03f.title: <player>
25cfbcd1-f83e-4342-bd69-7cce8f38b03f.text: You mean you don't have it?

04d69545-35fd-4f2b-8833-2d7a1e14d316.title: Sir Prysin
04d69545-35fd-4f2b-8833-2d7a1e14d316.text:
Oh I do have it, but it is so powerful that the king
made me put it in a special box which needs three
different keys to open it. That way it won't fall into the

options.text: So give me the keys!
And why is this a problem?

66f3422f-9994-41ca-b632-19625bb072a9.title: Sir Prysin
66f3422f-9994-41ca-b632-19625bb072a9.text: Um, well, it's not so easy.

6b3b4aff-d5ab-460f-a9ea-9608522653af.title: Sir Prysin
6b3b4aff-d5ab-460f-a9ea-9608522653af.text:
I kept one of the keys. I gave the other two to other
people for safe keeping.

6bda4f93-841c-4418-9cc3-64d8d6d537eb.title: Sir Prysin
6bda4f93-841c-4418-9cc3-64d8d6d537eb.text: One I gave to Rovin, the captain of the palace guard.

f923a1d1-d67c-4c65-9069-973ee56855da.title: Sir Prysin
f923a1d1-d67c-4c65-9069-973ee56855da.text: I gave the other to the wizard Traiborn.

e809ae6d-cfd7-47c2-871f-f7f30af8638e.title: <player>
e809ae6d-cfd7-47c2-871f-f7f30af8638e.text: He's back and unfortunately I've got to deal with him.

08251d81-6a2d-469d-a9f0-4cab5371db8d.title: <player>
08251d81-6a2d-469d-a9f0-4cab5371db8d.text:
You don't look up to much. I suppose Silverlight may be
good enough to carry you through though.

b6325922-08e6-4d3d-9821-e41e69fde475.title: <player>
b6325922-08e6-4d3d-9821-e41e69fde475.text: And why is this a problem?

c8f82976-ca7e-4aa8-8c24-a8262590343e.title: Sir Prysin
c8f82976-ca7e-4aa8-8c24-a8262590343e.text: So how are you doing with getting the keys?

136b5132-ebcd-42c9-99cd-d72e4fd59708.title: <player>
136b5132-ebcd-42c9-99cd-d72e4fd59708.text: I have found some of them.

6463b605-4700-4e3a-ad4d-e1039231257c.title: <player>
6463b605-4700-4e3a-ad4d-e1039231257c.text: I haven't found any of them yet.

options.text: Can you remind me where all the keys were again?
I'm still looking.

3167e190-bb04-46d2-973c-d2032d49ad36.title: <player>
3167e190-bb04-46d2-973c-d2032d49ad36.text: Can you remind me where all the keys were again?

11aeee97-66a5-484d-9b6b-ab1d32dea3ed.title: Sir Prysin
11aeee97-66a5-484d-9b6b-ab1d32dea3ed.text:
I kept one of the keys. I gave the other two to other
people for safe keeping.

317bf8ae-2b67-4f21-95cf-525d560b7346.title: Sir Prysin
317bf8ae-2b67-4f21-95cf-525d560b7346.text: One I gave to Rovin, the captain of the palace guard.

96996f1b-fba7-4315-9ad3-37daaeeb2885.title: Sir Prysin
96996f1b-fba7-4315-9ad3-37daaeeb2885.text: I gave the other to the wizard Traiborn.

options.text: Can you give me your key?
Where can I find Captain Rovin?
Where does the wizard live?

d7982cb2-e10c-4a5b-9834-2e0241da65af.title: <player>
d7982cb2-e10c-4a5b-9834-2e0241da65af.text: Can you give me your key?

5f3c4a25-aa9e-48a3-9a9f-cc79d5bdae70.title: Sir Prysin
5f3c4a25-aa9e-48a3-9a9f-cc79d5bdae70.text: Well there's a problem there as well.

77b60cbc-9675-41a0-a622-59d3e456c2e6.title: Sir Prysin
77b60cbc-9675-41a0-a622-59d3e456c2e6.text:
I managed to drop the key in the drain just outside the
palace kitchen. It is just inside and I can't reach it.

options.text: So what does the drain lead to?
Where can I find Captain Rovin?
Where does the wizard live?

4c70bd11-5ee2-4aae-bdc6-3d59179f2dee.title: <player>
4c70bd11-5ee2-4aae-bdc6-3d59179f2dee.text: So what does the drain connect to?

0c381f92-b56f-4a8d-aac9-755e624b9683.title: Sir Prysin
0c381f92-b56f-4a8d-aac9-755e624b9683.text:
It is the drain for the drainpipe running from the sink
in the kitchen down to the palace sewers.

options.text: Where can I find Captain Rovin?
Where does the wizard live?
Well I'd better go key hunting.
Can you give me your key?
Where does the wizard live?
Well I'd better go key hunting.

983e7dfc-59b7-45e7-92c5-fa0e1a4bf4f7.title: <player>
983e7dfc-59b7-45e7-92c5-fa0e1a4bf4f7.text: Where can I find Captain Rovin?

27dc0549-8439-4ede-b28b-a75bb2cb9c28.title: Sir Prysin
27dc0549-8439-4ede-b28b-a75bb2cb9c28.text:
Captain Rovin lives at the top of the guards' quarters in
the north-west wing of this palace.

cfe1afe3-b854-44bd-b647-f46bb7ad2ca2.title: <player>
cfe1afe3-b854-44bd-b647-f46bb7ad2ca2.text: Well I'd better go key hunting.

d71c55d1-8cc9-47f2-bed9-d85a6a9d3529.title: Sir Prysin
d71c55d1-8cc9-47f2-bed9-d85a6a9d3529.text: Ok, tell me when you've got them all.

14946c2a-4d76-4045-a004-5a49389a39be.title: Sir Prysin
14946c2a-4d76-4045-a004-5a49389a39be.text:
He is one of the wizards who lives in the tower on the
little island just off the south coast. I believe his
quarters are on the first floor of the tower.

options.text: Can you give me your key?
Where can I find Captain Rovin?
Well I'd better go key hunting.

1a72af42-4c2a-4dfb-9086-9d4e6c37f1b0.title: Sir Prysin
1a72af42-4c2a-4dfb-9086-9d4e6c37f1b0.text: Excellent! Now I can give you Silverlight.

39042502-abb5-4ddd-93da-0ee86652946d.text: Sir Prysin hands you a very shiny sword.

f5e13464-f643-4d1f-a75a-e23d40d01dba.title: Sir Prysin
f5e13464-f643-4d1f-a75a-e23d40d01dba.text:
That sword belonged to my great-grandfather. Make
sure you treat it with respect!

ab70237c-a705-4f86-adb0-bda58785686a.title: Note
ab70237c-a705-4f86-adb0-bda58785686a.text: If already has silverlight, tell to go kill delrith?

dc42448f-e4a3-4d61-ab46-d8e9f277601f.title: Sir Prysin
dc42448f-e4a3-4d61-ab46-d8e9f277601f.text: Have you sorted that demon out yet?

e9270c23-ce7b-4d59-ad43-4e1f66ae597c.title: <player>
e9270c23-ce7b-4d59-ad43-4e1f66ae597c.text: Not yet. And I, um, lost Silverlight.

07f9c2bc-1621-4b16-b89c-06251f446f48.title: Sir Prysin
07f9c2bc-1621-4b16-b89c-06251f446f48.text:
Yes, I know, someone returned it to me. Take better
care of it this time.

42984c7e-af1e-4d7b-b871-4ddac2efb637.title: Sir Prysin
42984c7e-af1e-4d7b-b871-4ddac2efb637.text: A good job well done then.

9c59439d-e982-479f-a84c-b7ead2466c1d.title: Sir Prysin
9c59439d-e982-479f-a84c-b7ead2466c1d.text: Hello. I've heard you stopped the demon, well done.

options.text: Yes, that's right.
Yes, although I'm afraid I've lost Silverlight.

20eae3b2-ee65-4e78-b0e1-dc77e812fd38.title: <player>
20eae3b2-ee65-4e78-b0e1-dc77e812fd38.text: Yes, although I'm afraid I've lost Silverlight.

c45b43c8-ccfd-42bd-801b-5b880c29b7ba.title: Sir Prysin
c45b43c8-ccfd-42bd-801b-5b880c29b7ba.text:
Yes, news of your carelessness is almost as widespread
as knowledge of your victory. Fortunately for you, the
sword has come back into my possession.

options.text: Phew, that's a relief.
Is there any chance of me borrowing it again?

a147ccbe-f4d1-4e73-b8b9-e97621a15d5d.title: <player>
a147ccbe-f4d1-4e73-b8b9-e97621a15d5d.text: Is there any chance of me borrowing it again?

82fbe8f6-b324-4e07-92a5-090d148d59f3.title: Sir Prysin
82fbe8f6-b324-4e07-92a5-090d148d59f3.text:
I'm not going to give it away that easily again, it's far
too important to be treated so disrespectfully.

a85c5bda-1d8c-4995-9706-e6f2096433d3.title: Sir Prysin
a85c5bda-1d8c-4995-9706-e6f2096433d3.text:
If you wish to make use of Silverlight again, it will cost
you 500 coins. Maybe that will encourage you to look
after it.

options.text: No way, it's not worth that much.
Okay, I'll pay.

aec875dd-5221-4b45-833c-2484c89f6e9f.title: <player>
aec875dd-5221-4b45-833c-2484c89f6e9f.text: No way, it's not worth that much.

5ca0e3c9-3860-47ce-a05d-b9c7022bc58c.title: Sir Prysin
5ca0e3c9-3860-47ce-a05d-b9c7022bc58c.text:
I'll be here when you actually have that much money to
pay me.

3b41b01c-119e-486c-973f-4e4a15c4d3b5.title: Sir Prysin
3b41b01c-119e-486c-973f-4e4a15c4d3b5.text: May you make good use of it.
